cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use mtrnafeat in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "mtrnafeat: Mitochondrial mRNA structural-feature analysis"
abstract: >-
  Downstream analysis toolkit for mitochondrial mRNA secondary-structure
  features. Consumes DMS-MaPseq-derived dot-bracket structures and pairs
  them with thermodynamic predictions (ViennaRNA, RNAstructure, RNAplfold)
  to compare experimental and modeled local pairing, call regions of
  experimental-vs-thermodynamic divergence, and quantify codon-substitution
  thermodynamics across mt-mRNAs in human and yeast.
type: software
authors:
